    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would make a reliable budget-friendly option for someone willing to put in a little work. The engine and transmission are functional, though you may notice some minor fluid seepage and the ride isn't as quiet as it once was. The exterior shows its age with several noticeable scratches, some fading in the clear coat, and a few small dings. Inside, the upholstery has some visible wear and staining, and while most electronics work, the passenger side window is slow to operate. It is a solid runner that gets you from A to B, but it is certainly not in showroom condition.",
      "price": 19500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "fair",
