      "description": "We are privileged to offer this exemplary vehicle, currently presented in showroom condition. This unit has been maintained to an exacting standard, exhibiting no discernible wear and reflecting a history of meticulous stewardship. From the flawless exterior finish to the pristine interior appointments, every aspect of this automobile remains in peak form. This is a rare opportunity to acquire a vehicle that delivers a driving experience indistinguishable from its original delivery state. An inspection will confirm its status as a premier example of its class.",
      "price": 48500.0,
